<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Upload Success - <%= siteTitle %></title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #4CAF50;
        }
        h2 {
            color: #555;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        .success-banner {
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #e8f5e9;
            border-left: 4px solid #4CAF50;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .info-box {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .info-box strong {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #333;
        }
        .code-display {
            background-color: #fff;
            border: 2px solid #4CAF50;
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 15px;
            font-family: monospace;
            font-size: 16px;
            word-break: break-all;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .warning {
            padding: 15px;
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border-left: 4px solid #ff9800;
            color: #856404;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .button-link {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #2196F3;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .button-link:hover {
            background-color: #0b7dda;
        }
        a {
            color: #2196F3;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        hr {
            margin: 40px 0;
            border: none;
            border-top: 2px solid #eee;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>✓ File Upload Successful!</h1>
    
    <div class="success-banner">
        Your file "<strong><%= filename %></strong>" has been uploaded successfully.
    </div>
    
    <h2>Important Information</h2>
    
    <div class="info-box">
        <strong>File UUID:</strong>
        <div class="code-display"><%= uuid %></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="info-box">
        <strong>TOTP Secret (Base32):</strong>
        <div class="code-display"><%= totpSecret %></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="warning">
        <strong>⚠ Important:</strong> Save both the UUID and TOTP secret to download your file later. 
        Add the TOTP secret to your authenticator app (Google Authenticator, Authy, etc.) to generate codes for downloading.
    </div>
    
    <h2>Next Steps</h2>
    <p>
        <a href="/download/<%= uuid %>" class="button-link">Download Your File Now</a>
    </p>
    
    <hr>
    
    <p>
        <a href="/">← Upload another file</a> | 
        <a href="/totp-test">Test TOTP Generator</a>
    </p>
</body>
</html>
